title: Disgaea Custom Soundtrack
description:
The Disgaea Custom Soundtrack that is included with the Playstation 3 game Disgaea 3. The tracks are as follows:

1: Demon Academy
2: Demon Academy Prospective Student
3: Tales of Innocent Youth
4: Lord Laharl's... Hymn?
5: Galaxy Wars
6: Planet X
7: Etna Boogie
8: Poem of the Vagabond
9: Sinful Rose
10: My Comrade
11: Rock Crystal
12: Etna Rock
13: Twinkle Star
14: Disgaea Rhapsody
15: Extreme Outlaw Overlord
16: White Tiger
17: Running Fire
18: Dark Whisper
19: Makai Fugue
20: Demon Academy Alma master
21: Lord Laharl's Hymn

The CD is compromised of selections from all three Disgaea games.
From Disgaea: Hour of Darkness: 5, 6, 7, 10, 17, 18, 21.
From Disgaea 2: Cursed Memories: 4, 9, 12, 13, 14, 16.
From Disgaea 3: Absence of Justice: 1, 2, 3, 8, 11, 15, 19, 20.

Enjoy and please seed!
